  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to compare the post-discharge growth of preterm infants fed
      with 2 different post discharge formulas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Infants will be randomized upon discharge from the NICU. We will follow weight, height and
      head circumference for three months following discharge, In addition any feeding difficulties
      will be noted.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
